{"title":"新兵","authors":["水秀"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":7,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水秀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿三号军装嫌大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶亮的眼睛成天直眨巴；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脑子装着问号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚戴上领章就吵着要打靶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长发给他一支冲锋枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐得他心里开了花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙从背包里掏出新手绢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把这支枪擦了又擦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天，握着枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在野地里摸、爬、滚、打；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚，挎着枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和班长走绝壁，攀悬崖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入伍不到半年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就炼成了个“铁疙瘩”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名叫小龙“龙”不“小”啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣榜上安了家！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}